|result = '''[[2013 Egyptian coup d'<U+00E9>tat]]'''
* Overthrow of [[Mohamed Morsi]] by the military, who is later placed in jail and faces trial.
* Head of the Constitutional Court [[Adly Mansour]] is appointed as acting president by General [[Abdel Fattah el-Sisi]]  until new scheduled elections.
* Arrest of senior Islamist figures in or outside of the government.
* Suspension of the Muslim Brotherhood-backed [[2012 Draft Constitution of Egypt|constitution of 2012]].
* [[Islamist unrest in Egypt (2013<U+2013>present)|Ongoing unrest]] in response to the coup.
